## Shared state (`.agent/`)

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.agent/status/<agent>.md` | Current agent state |
| `.agent/messages/<agent>.md` | Inbox (append only) |
| `.agent/backlog/tasks.md` | Backlog / In Progress / Done |
| `.agent/reports/heartbeat.md` | Manager check-in summary |

